@startuml
' Feature 018 partner-office sequence.
actor "Партнер-офис" as Office
actor "Логистический оператор" as Logistics
actor "Региональный менеджер" as Manager
participant "Frontend web-shell\n/partner-office/*" as FE
participant "partner-office Controller" as Controller
participant "partner-office Service" as Service
database "partner-office DB" as DB
participant "order module" as Order
participant "claim workflow" as Claim
participant "delivery/pickup workflow" as Delivery
participant "WMS/1C adapter" as WMS

Office -> FE : Открывает /partner-office/all-orders
FE -> Controller : GET /api/partner-office/orders\nX-User-Context-Id
Controller -> Service : searchOrders(filters, userContext)
Service -> DB : load office orders page
Service -> Order : enrich order references
Service -> Delivery : enrich delivery and pickup links
Service --> Controller : PartnerOfficeOrderPageResponse
Controller --> FE : 200 JSON
FE --> Office : Список заказов, статусы, supplyId, deviation

Office -> FE : Открывает /partner-office/supply/BOG-SUP-018-001
FE -> Controller : GET /api/partner-office/supply/{supplyId}
Controller -> Service : getSupplyDetails(supplyId, userContext)
Service -> DB : load supply, orders, items, movements, deviations
Service -> WMS : optional latest external status snapshot
Service --> Controller : PartnerOfficeSupplyDetailsResponse
Controller --> FE : 200 JSON
FE --> Office : Карточка supply, timeline, actions

Logistics -> FE : Выполняет transition ARRIVED
FE -> Controller : POST /api/partner-office/supply/{supplyId}/transition\nIdempotency-Key
Controller -> Service : transitionSupply(targetStatus, reason)
Service -> DB : validate lifecycle and persist status movement
Service --> Controller : STR_MNEMO_PARTNER_OFFICE_SUPPLY_STATUS_UPDATED
Controller --> FE : 200 SupplyActionResponse
FE --> Logistics : Локализованное сообщение из i18n

Office -> FE : Фиксирует недостачу по заказу
FE -> Controller : POST /api/partner-office/supply/orders/{orderNumber}/deviations
Controller -> Service : recordDeviation(request, userContext)
Service -> DB : persist deviation and movement
Service -> Claim : expose claim reference data
Service --> Controller : STR_MNEMO_PARTNER_OFFICE_DEVIATION_RECORDED
Controller --> FE : 200 SupplyActionResponse
FE --> Office : Отклонение видно в карточке заказа

Manager -> FE : Открывает /partner-office/report
FE -> Controller : GET /api/partner-office/report
Controller -> Service : buildReport(filters, userContext)
Service -> DB : aggregate SLA, shortages, damaged, escalations
Service --> Controller : PartnerOfficeReportResponse
Controller --> FE : 200 JSON
FE --> Manager : KPI, проблемные маршруты и эскалации

Office -> FE : Запрашивает чужой supply
FE -> Controller : GET /api/partner-office/supply/foreign
Controller -> Service : getSupplyDetails(foreign, userContext)
Service -> DB : check access by officeId/regionId
Service --> Controller : access denied
Controller --> FE : 403 STR_MNEMO_PARTNER_OFFICE_ACCESS_DENIED
FE --> Office : Локализованное сообщение без раскрытия данных
@enduml
